    "description": "Hear ye, hear ye! We cordially invite you to take a peek behind the veil of Gatherac with this brand-new Baladins art book!<br><br>Within, you’ll be able to see the original designs of your favorite adventurers and how they transformed from the beginning to now. But be warned, there are <strong>major spoilers</strong> present in this art book, so proceed with caution!<br><br><strong>To access the artbook after purchase:</strong> Ensure you have the base game &quot;Baladins&quot; installed and updated. Find &quot;Baladins&quot; in your Steam Library list, right-click on it, then navigate to &quot;Manage&quot; → &quot;Browse local files&quot;. There, you should see a folder titled &quot;Baladins_DigitalArtbook&quot;, which contains the artbook itself, as a PDF file with the same name!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076230/extras/22220c75d207f05a6299cbf19223997a.avif?t=1721664053\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
